ty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kindamorphic/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723532-high-quality-dividend-stock-universe-factset-research-systems-shows-attractive-valuation\">my coverage</a> on FactSet Research Systems (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FDS\" title=\"FactSet Research Systems Inc.\">FDS</a></span>) in Sept\u201924, which I recommended a buy rating given the clear growth runway ahead of FDS, supported by the Fed cutting rates, this post is to provide</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156385097/image_2156385097.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745478-factset-research-systems-stock-q1-confident-low-teens-eps-growth-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 06:51:00"}, {"id": "4745475", "title": "Dave: An Old-School Payday Lender In Disguise", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='gold coins and a neon billboard displaying the words \"PAYDAY LOANS\"' data-id=\"2165047379\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Love Employee/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As credit <a href=\"https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/REVOLSL\" rel=\"nofollow\">card debt levels soar</a>, many seek new ways to borrow money. In recent years, we've seen the rise of numerous fintech companies focused on changing personal lending. As I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4728494-affirm-stock-buy-now-pay-later-may-be-superior-credit-card-lending\">previously discussed</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165047379/image_2165047379.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745475-dave-stock-old-school-payday-lender-in-disguise-reasonably-valued", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 06:09:29"}, {"id": "4745474", "title": "Tracking John Paulson's Paulson & Company Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/531467608/image_531467608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CDS cubics acronym\" data-id=\"531467608\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn