"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745471-ibhf-fixed-maturity-etf-love", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 05:07:16"}, {"id": "4745465", "title": "Hapag-Lloyd: A Look Beneath The Surface", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Crane operator picking up a Hapag-Lloyd sea container\" data-id=\"1817176691\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">VanderWolf-Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Hapag-Lloyd Aktiengesellschaft (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HLAGF\" title=\"Hapag-Lloyd Aktiengesellschaft\">OTCPK:HLAGF</a>), a top-five container shipping company primarily focused on European routes (Transatlantic and Europe-Asia), recently released an <a href=\"https://www.hapag-lloyd.com/content/dam/website/downloads/ir/HLAG_9M_2024_EN.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">upbeat interim report for Q3 2024</a> and raised full-year guidance on the back of this strength. This came</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817176691/image_1817176691.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745465-hapag-lloyd-stock-look-beneath-the-surface-reiterate-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:45:54"}, {"id": "4745462", "title": "British American Tobacco: The Ideal Company To Face An Uncertain 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Girl smoking\" data-id=\"626868346\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">markophotoart/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Fed's decision to cut rates only twice in 2025 has sown doubts among investors. High rates for longer means limiting economic growth and not giving a boost to demand for credit. The decision was made on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/626868346/image_626868346.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745462-british-american-tobacco-ideal-company-to-face-uncertain-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:19:06"}, {"id": "4745458", "title": "Descartes: The Quiet Canadian Compounder - Why Descartes Remains My Top Software Pick", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Global Communication Network (World Map Credits To Nasa)\" data-id=\"1329183101\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction </strong></h2> <p>Descartes Systems (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DSGX\" title=\"The Descartes Systems Group Inc.\">DSGX</a></span>) was the first company I covered here on Seeking Alpha. Interestingly, it was also the first stock I pitched to my Boss a few years ago during my time as a Fund Manager Assistant at</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329183101/image_1329183101.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745458-descartes-quiet-canadian-compounder-my-top-software-pick-strong-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 04:06:36"}, {"id": "4745469", "title": "Q3 GDP Third Estimate: Real GDP At 3.1%, Above Forecast", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gross domestic product or GDP. Business, economy, trade, Consumption, and Investment. An arrow sign pointing downwards and up in a wooden block\" data-id=\"1496930327\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496930327/image_1496930327.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/